snippet.title: ENENRA: DΔEMON CORE - UE5 HACK AND SLASH GAME
snippet.description:
ENENRA : DΔEMON CORE is a third person, hack & slash game, with an emphasis on abilities and cinematic combat. 

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1963690/ENENRA_DEMON_CORE/
Follow the project: https://twitter.com/ENENRAGame
Support on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/ENENRA

Developed in Unreal Engine 5.1
Music - https://youtu.be/UeAK6P7Gl7w?si=0fE-Klps6lfsnDBC
